{
  "stem": "162.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when you go to school in Germany, you carry a sweet bag.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's called a tute.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it's-- it's like a cone, like a huge cone.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the more money you have and-- and-- and the more generous your parents are, the bigger is the cone.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And it's filled with goodies and gifts and-- and sweets and all of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I remember going to school very proudly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I spent--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This is the first day at school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's like a present that you get for the first day of school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I lived with my grandmother in those days.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I remember my aunt and uncle, my aunt, Dolly, and my uncle, Bruno.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the meantime, I found out that one of the uncles who was in Germany immigrated to London, England.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He emigrated to England.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My Uncle Bruno and my Aunt Dolly did not-- she did not want to leave Berlin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She believed that they would be saved, that nothing would happen to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they ended up as one of the last Jews in Berlin, the people who walked around with the yellow star and the people who tried to hide till the very end.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And my aunt tells me this story that one of the friends that my uncle had, they were doing some black market things in order to keep themselves alive because they had to live quietly, and they had to live in hiding.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day, my uncle went out, and he-- the very friend that he used to work with betrayed him and turned him in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And my uncle ended up in Auschwitz in a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
